I denne forskriften menes med:
Sertifiseringsforordningen: Commission Regulation (EC) No 1702/2003 for the airworthiness and environmental certification of aircraft and related products, parts and appliances, as well as for the certification of design and production organisations, med vedlegg og appendikser;
Part 21: Vedlegg til sertifiseringsforordningen.
